high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the small black bin to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the sponge out of the small black bin.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the side of the kitchen island.
Pick the sponge on the closest white plate on the kitchen island.
Pick up the white plate with the sponge on it.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk around the kitchen island to the section of counter to the right of the oven and look up.
Open the cabinet door to the right of the microwave and put the plate with the sponge on it in the cabinet then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a white plate with a sponge on it in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the bin on the floor, to the right of the fridge.
Take the sponge out of the bin.
Turn around and veer right after reaching the kitchen island, then face the island, the side of it with the two black stools.
Place the sponge on the white plate closest to the edge of the table.
Pick up the plate.
Walk left and towards the stove, stopping at the counter just to the right of the stove.
Place the plate in the cabinet to the right of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a sponge on it in a cabinet.
